                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="speaker-card">
                <img class="speaker-image" src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x450?text=Speaker+6" alt="Speaker 6">
                <div class="speaker-content">
                    <span class="speaker-role">Japan</span>
                    <h3 class="speaker-name">Prof. K. Inazu</h3>
                    <p class="speaker-affiliation">National Institute of Technology (KOSEN), Numazu College</p>
                    <p class="speaker-bio">
                        Prof. K. Inazu is a researcher in chemistry and biochemistry, focusing on functional materials and catalytic systems for energy and environmental applications. 
                        His work contributes to the development of sustainable processes and innovative materials supporting green energy technologies.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="speaker-card">
