                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="speaker-card">
                <img class="speaker-image" src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x450?text=Speaker+9" alt="Speaker 9">
                <div class="speaker-content">
                    <span class="speaker-role">Canada</span>
                    <h3 class="speaker-name">Prof. Dan V. Nicolau</h3>
                    <p class="speaker-affiliation">
